title: Converse CONS Project : Paris
description:
10 days of skating and creativity, including skate photography and board shaping workshops.

Featuring Ilk, Remy Taveira, Jerome Campbell, Kevin Rodrigues and Felipe Bartolome.

Music by Birth of Joy. Track Devil's Paradise.
